						<p><hi rend="bold">King: Rājarāja III Year 21: 1237 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged at the end. It records the provision made for a full-length flowergarland and services at four <hi rend="italic">sandhis</hi> to god Tiruvoṟṟiyūr-nāyiṉār at Tiruvoṟṟiyūr in Puḻar-koṭṭam in Jayaṅgoṇḍachoḻa-maṇḍalam by Oṟṟi Araśan, son of Paiyyūrnāḍ-āḻvār Vaḷaiyamaḻagiyār. </p>						

